ActFood and Drugs Act
PrecisRegulations Amending the FOOD AND DRUG REGULATIONS (1197 - SETHOXYDIM) by setting maximum limits on residues (MRLs) of this herbicide and its metabolites resulting from its use on asparagus, blueberries, carrots, flax, peppers, pumpkins, raspberries, strawberries, sunflowers and turnips, by raising the limits for cranberries and lentils, and by setting a limit for mustard.
